    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIRCAL\nSYSTEM TIMETABLE\nEffective October 31, 1982\nLOW FARES to 15 CITIES",
      "CHECK OUR LOW FARES\nAIRCAL\nAirCal offers everyday low fares to 15 cities throughout the\nWest. Combined with great savings is a style of service that you\nexpect. Convenient schedules. One stop check in. Seat selec-\ntion on every flight. Speedy baggage handling. One of the best\non-time records. And a staff of trained professionals who care\nabout getting you where you are going!\nour style"
